Subject: [PATCH] drm/amdgpu/gfx: disable gfx9 cp_ecc_error_irq only when
 enabling legacy gfx ras
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 6.1.29
Git-commit: 4a76680311330aefe5074bed8f06afa354b85c48

commit 4a76680311330aefe5074bed8f06afa354b85c48 upstream.

